  "instructions": [
    "Heat the butter in a medium saucepan over medium heat until melted.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the thyme and parsley and cook for 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add the rice and stir to coat with the butter mixture.",
    "Add the chicken broth and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cover the saucepan with a lid.",
    "Simmer for 18-20 minutes until the liquid is absorbed and the rice is tender.",
    "Fluff the rice with a fork and stir in the lemon juice and salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley and serve hot."
